gobblin.data.management.retention.dataset

Class ConfigurableDataset<T extends DatasetVersion>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.data.management.retention.dataset.DatasetBase<T>
      • gobblin.data.management.retention.dataset.ConfigurableDataset<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CleanableDataset, Dataset

    public class ConfigurableDataset<T extends DatasetVersion>
extends DatasetBase<T>
    DatasetBase that instantiates VersionFinder and RetentionPolicy from classes read from an input Properties.

    The class of VersionFinder should be under key VERSION_FINDER_CLASS_KEY, while the class of RetentionPolicy should be under key RETENTION_POLICY_CLASS_KEY.
